		"startIntroPart1": "All hail the Professor, leader of The Academy! When the Great Catastrophe shattered the old world, a group of university professors, scientists, and philosophers barricaded themselves inside a sprawling campus complex. While others fought over canned food, they debated how to prevent the same mistakes from destroying humanity again. Over the generations, The Academy became a beacon of learning in the wasteland - training doctors, engineers, and thinkers, and sending them out to rebuild what was lost. Their motto carved above the gates reads: 'We fell because we forgot. We rise because we remember.'",
