        "startIntroPart1": "All praise to the Architect, leader of The Builders! When the Great Catastrophe toppled skyscrapers and cracked highways into dust, most survivors huddled in caves and ruins. But the Architect and a band of construction workers, civil engineers, and urban planners saw opportunity in the rubble. They began salvaging concrete, rebar, and glass to erect the first new structures the wasteland had seen in generations. The Builders do not merely survive - they construct. Walls, bridges, water systems, shelters - wherever The Builders go, civilization follows, rising from the ground like monuments to human will.",
        "startIntroPart2": "Architect, your blueprints are drawn and your crews stand ready. Every beam you raise is a declaration that humanity refuses to live in ruins forever. Will you lay the foundations of a new world from the wreckage of the old? Will EmpireForge stand as a monument built by your hands?",

