        "startIntroPart1": "Hail the Warden, sovereign of The North! When the Great Catastrophe plunged the world into chaos, the frozen territories became both prison and sanctuary. Where others saw only ice and death, the Warden saw vast untapped resources buried beneath permafrost and snow. The North controls enormous stretches of territory rich in timber, ore, and fuel - resources that every faction desperately needs. Hardened by brutal winters and endless darkness, the people of The North are survivors without equal, their iron will forged in the coldest crucible on earth.",
