        "startIntroPart1": "Welcome the Merchant, master of The Caravan! When the Great Catastrophe turned cities to ash and severed all supply lines, one group refused to stay put. The Merchant gathered traders, drivers, and nomads into a vast convoy of armored trucks and pack animals that crisscrosses the wasteland, connecting isolated survivor camps with the goods they need to live. The Caravan knows every safe route, every hidden cache, and every faction's price. They are the lifeblood of the post-apocalyptic economy - without them, settlements wither and die. Where The Caravan stops, markets spring up. Where they leave, silence follows.",
