        "startIntroPart1": "All hail the Diver, master of The Scavengers! When the Great Catastrophe buried the old world under rubble and toxic dust, most survivors saw only desolation. But the Diver saw a treasure trove. Leading teams of ruin divers, salvage experts, and fearless scrappers into the most dangerous collapsed structures, The Scavengers pull resources from the bones of the dead world. No ruin is too unstable, no basement too flooded, no factory too irradiated for their crews. They strip buildings to their foundations, recycle every scrap of metal, and turn the garbage of the old world into the gold of the new. What others abandon, The Scavengers claim.",
