        "startIntroPart1": "All hail the Climber, sovereign of The Mountain! When the Great Catastrophe forced survivors to flee the poisoned lowlands, one faction retreated to the highest ground they could find. The Climber led a band of mountaineers, miners, and engineers to the peaks, where they carved fortresses into the living rock. The Mountain faction is nearly impossible to assault - their settlements cling to cliffsides, their lookouts see enemies approaching from miles away, and their passes are death traps for any invader. Rich mineral deposits in the highland caves provide all the metal and stone they need, while mountain springs offer the cleanest water in the wasteland.",
