        "startIntroPart1": "Fear the Raider, warlord of The Raiders! When the Great Catastrophe stripped the world bare, while others mourned, The Raiders saw opportunity. The Raider gathered the most aggressive, fearless, and ruthless survivors into roving war bands that strike settlements, strip them of resources, and vanish before retaliation arrives. They do not build - they take. They do not farm - they raid. Armored in scrap metal and wielding brutal improvised weapons, The Raiders are the nightmare of every peaceful settlement in the wasteland. Their war cries echo across the ruins, and their bonfires light up the night after every successful plunder.",
